Class AccessEncounterServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openmrs.api.impl.BaseOpenmrsService
      • org.openmrs.module.usagestatistics668.impl.AccessEncounterServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openmrs.api.OpenmrsService, AccessEncounterService

    public class AccessEncounterServiceImpl
extends org.openmrs.api.impl.BaseOpenmrsService
implements AccessEncounterService
    Implementation of our NoteService interface. This class is set in the /metadata/moduleApplicationContext.xml file to be matched to the NoteService interface.

    This class extends BaseOpenmrsService so that there are empty methods for onStartup and onShutdown. This allows sheilds us from changes to the OpenmrsService interface from forcing us to implement the methods.

    NEVER call "new NoteServiceImpl()....". To use this class, you do:
    Context.getService(NoteService.class).saveNote(note)...
    Author:
    Anthony Lee
